Author: zeleaa
Text: dude recovery has made my stomach hurt SO bad EVERY day. doctor ran quite a few tests. no, nothing wrong, she said. ok so why do i feel sharp pains after eating one (1) packet of oatmeal? i spend a great deal of my day in bed with a heating pack on my tum bc it’s the only thing that works :/
